---
title: Turkey-Rosemary Meatballs and Onion Gravy with Smashed Potatoes and Sugar Snap Peas
description: In this meal, classic stew flavours get condensed into a quick 30-minute recipe. Creamy mash cradles rosemary-studded meatballs doused in savoury onion gravy. Crisp sweet peas bring it all together.
